title: Julia Eddelbuettel
text:
About Me
I am a Senior Statistical Programmer Analyst in the Department of Health Policy and Management at the Johns Hopkins Bloomberg School of Public Health.
I am interested in health policy research related to mental health, substance use, and maternal & infant health.
